@{b}C2B()@{ub}

Usage:@{b}C2B(string)@{ub}

Converts the character string into the equivalent string of binary digits.

See also: @{"C2X()" LINK "C2X/main"}

Example:
@{fg shine}
        say c2b('abc')                  ==>011000010110001001100011
@{fg text}
